## Copy this file to about.inc (same directory) to take over the About page
## prose. When about.inc exists, it replaces the Extras.about text; delete it
## to fall back. Plain HTML, and WeeWX tags like $station.* are expanded.
<p>
  Welcome to the aganet.gr weather station in Kamena Vourla, Greece. It has been
  recording since the station went online and updates every few minutes.
</p>
<p>
  Hardware: <b>$station.hardware</b>. Running WeeWX $station.version.
</p>
<p>
  Questions or corrections? Reach me at
  <a href="https://anegio.com" rel="noopener">anegio.com</a>.
</p>
